{
  "stem": "13096.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And another thing, you know, my sister, beside that time she went to hospital, she was there-- she was taken by the-- the-- we used to call the malady of the camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It means the-- the-- the sickness of the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That is as much hungry as you are aware all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When the sickness of the camp grabs you, it was like a disease, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then you have lost your appetite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You don't want to eat anything else, even if they give you the best food in the world.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's like anorexia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When you drink, you know, when you a certain-- when you can't eat anymore, the same thing happened in the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The certain, you know, time when you were so much sick, you're couldn't eat anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then you stay one day or two day without food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually you die.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because that it was the fate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody was trying to eat, even you know, when they were sick, and to push the other friends that they were sick, of this sickness, not to abandon hope and to abandon, you know, the food.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one or two times, my sister was-- was caught, you know, by this disease.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't want to eat, my older sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So myself also, with my little sister, she was there, we had two-- the three ration.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister wouldn't eat her ration.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took her ration of bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to the kitchen and-- and there were those girls working there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I give the ration of one-- of one-- of day if she can give me one clove of garlic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because this garlic, you know, in Rhodes Island, we used to use so much in our cuisine.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
